《'''年度最佳學生'''》（'''Student of the Year'''）是2012年的[[印度電影|印度電影]]，由[[卡蘭·喬哈|卡蘭·喬哈]]導演，是一部愛情喜劇。此片起用了新人作主要角色，但也有請來知名影星客串。<ref>[https://www.masala.com/transformation-tuesday-stars-of-student-of-the-year-then-vs-now-279116.html “Transformation Tuesday: Stars of Student of the Year, Then Vs. Now”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.masala.com/transformation-tuesday-stars-of-student-of-the-year-then-vs-now-279116.html |date=20190411235243 }}. Masala! [09-04-2019].</ref>

